The contribution rate of a member who is subject to the Alternate Contributory Pension Selection under Part III of this subtitle is:
3% of the member's earnable compensation received from July 1, 2006 to June 30, 2007, both inclusive;
4% of the member's earnable compensation received from July 1, 2007 to June 30, 2008, both inclusive;
5% of the member's earnable compensation received from July 1, 2008 to June 30, 2011, both inclusive; and
7% of the member's earnable compensation received on or after July 1, 2011.
